{"title":"linux下配置gradle环境","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.013Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/linux下配置gradle环境","updated":"2023-07-28T09:13:43.772Z","content":"<h2 id=\"linux下配置gradle环境\">linux下配置gradle环境<a title=\"#linux下配置gradle环境\" href=\"#linux下配置gradle环境\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>环境需求：<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/114478601?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501\" target=\"_blank\">安装java环境</a></strong>，可以参考<a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u014292402/article/details/114478601?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501\" target=\"_blank\">这篇文章</a></p>\n<p>1、首先去官网<a href=\"https://gradle.org/releases/\" target=\"_blank\">下载gradle安装包</a><br>\n下好包后解压在本地</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir gradle</span><br><span class=\"line\">unzip -d gradle gradle-7.3-all.zip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/936bdff921964efb95d5552573ec5c62.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/32d4fde6f9d240f9b910a4e4a33a4af8.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n2、然后设置环境变量</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vi /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在文件末尾加上</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> GRADLE_HOME=/root/gradle/gradle-7.3（该路径要包含gradle的bin目录）</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> PATH=<span class=\"variable\">$GRADLE_HOME</span>/bin:<span class=\"variable\">$PATH</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/fb362da76bdd42f795ed01e5e0187b0c.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>按<code>esc</code>，输入<code>：wq</code>，保存退出<br>\n刷新配置文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">source</span> /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后输入<code>gradle -v</code>,查看版本信息<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2564493167674033a7ec9bd46f26d50d.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZHJvaWRzYW5zZmFsbGJhY2s,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA5bCP5p2wcw==,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n此时gradle安装完成。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"linux下切换系统默认python版本","link":"2023/07/28/linux下切换系统默认python版本"},"next":{"title":"linux下配置并运行stellar区块链的federation组件","link":"2023/07/28/linux下配置并运行stellar区块链的federation组件"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/linux下配置gradle环境/","toc":[{"id":"linux下配置gradle环境","title":"linux下配置gradle环境","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"217 字约 1 分钟"}